{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"38666-a-special-nest","title":"A Special Nest","description":"A bird is trying to build a nest for herself. But everywhere she builds a nest, something or the other disturbs her. What will she do?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kavita Singh"],"illustrators":["Partho Sengupta"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/38666-a-special-nest"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/100169/size3/6ba43714a19f5bc87346890ae7c45e3b.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/100169/size6/6ba43714a19f5bc87346890ae7c45e3b.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73445/size6/8df18fbfc40f05906d6923f189f72dce.jpg","text":"Winter is approaching. A bird decides to build a nest.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73446/size6/a6ca17edc0e1d17ba5536bb4f82d8086.jpg","text":"She gathers little twigs and builds her nest carefully.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73447/size6/b08b0b9557a8663833de7aa868b1e1f8.jpg","text":"After a lot of care and hard work, the nest is ready. It is warm and cosy.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73448/size6/94ebf74be59e60773834030998fe8ab4.jpg","text":"The bird is happy. She lies down and begins day-dreaming of a comfortable winter.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73449/size6/361cd87cae97e376198bdb5acfd690d0.jpg","text":"As she is about to fall asleep, she feels something shaking.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73450/size6/a91223ab418cd4f0bd3333bf236e568c.jpg","text":"The bird thinks, “Maybe the wind is shaking the nest a little.” \nBut the nest shakes and trembles and shakes some more.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73451/size6/0d4421a1fb8a7a6396036cb2bbc49881.jpg","text":"The bird flies out of the nest. The next moment, the nest falls to the ground.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73452/size6/779484f67124d04bafcde70804a1e967.jpg","text":"The bird sees an elephant using the tree to scratch her back. She is quite annoyed. \n“This is so rude of you, elephant!” she says to her angrily, and flies away.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73453/size6/1ab416669bdc73da1858266efa9f5835.jpg","text":"She begins to search for a new place. A place where elephants can't reach her.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73454/size6/69ad85ba9416f63f1c13afd6b033ef13.jpg","text":"She starts building a \nnew nest.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73455/size6/438efbd21a8f7ca2679594c7ba1e3a0c.jpg","text":"With care and hard work, she builds a home. Tired, she falls asleep.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73456/size6/70e48866f476df7302687733b5075564.jpg","text":"Just as she is about to close her eyes, she sees two big, round eyes. They are staring at her.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73457/size6/72f7f16ec798134b09a926aa5786fc61.jpg","text":"It's a painter.\nHe takes her nest and throws it away.\nThen he picks up a brush and\n starts painting the wall.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73458/size6/c4b0347344d809f8f8c26e963b634c7b.jpg","text":"The bird is very annoyed. “This is so rude of you, human!” she says to him angrily and flies away. \nHer heart is heavy with worry.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73459/size6/a8ddc0b98a153c359ea03c8b56a6d660.jpg","text":"As she flies, she sees a balloon floating in the air.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73460/size6/5a21600accb54b5cd4b04be001c3378b.jpg","text":"And another!","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73461/size6/2fbd87207edfcbfaf700c50c7f02eaf3.jpg","text":"She looks below and sees lots and lots of balloons!","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73463/size6/62341ec2e31a1d6731063780c048dc64.jpg","text":"The bird looks at the balloons and has an idea.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/73465/size6/e139864db196ad9ea38d6607bba2011c.jpg","text":"With care and hard work, she builds a new nest. \nThis time, nobody can disturb her.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":19,"words":281}}